
Metang	 A steel type Pokémon

When two BELDUM fuse together, METANG 
is formed.  The brains of the BELDUM 
are joined by a magnetic nervous system. 
 By linking its brains magnetically, 
this POKéMON generates strong psychokinetic 
power. 

	Evolution Chain
Beldum ► Metang ► Metagross

